1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 21=

3
00:00:45,700 --> 00:00:47,680
The Zhuang family's daughter
has already been found.

4
00:00:48,220 --> 00:00:51,020
She was promised that as long as
the shipment of opium was handed over,

5
00:00:51,260 --> 00:00:52,500
it would be destroyed.

6
00:00:53,260 --> 00:00:54,660
But it was only for show.

7
00:00:54,980 --> 00:00:57,100
The location of the opium
has already been revealed.

8
00:00:58,820 --> 00:00:59,660
What?

9
00:01:00,300 --> 00:01:01,620
The opium was found?

10
00:01:06,860 --> 00:01:07,860
Commander-in-Chief,

11
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:09,420
please dismiss everyone else.

12
00:01:14,380 --> 00:01:16,300
All of you wait downstairs
in the main hall.

13
00:01:22,380 --> 00:01:23,540
Now we can talk.

14
00:01:26,300 --> 00:01:27,140
Come in.

15
00:01:38,940 --> 00:01:41,180
Why do you look so familiar to me?

16
00:01:42,780 --> 00:01:43,980
Li Shuche.

17
00:01:45,020 --> 00:01:46,260
I look familiar to you?

18
00:01:47,100 --> 00:01:50,940
I'm the Zhuang family's daughter
you've been searching for all along.

19
00:01:52,100 --> 00:01:52,700
This...

20
00:01:53,100 --> 00:01:54,220
This can't be.

21
00:01:57,580 --> 00:01:58,980
I remember now.

22
00:01:59,100 --> 00:02:00,780
You're Xue Wan.

23
00:02:01,820 --> 00:02:04,020
How could you be Zhuang Yunqiu?

24
00:02:06,100 --> 00:02:06,740
Nianchi,

25
00:02:07,060 --> 00:02:08,460
what exactly is going on?

26
00:02:10,780 --> 00:02:12,260
Let me introduce myself again.

27
00:02:13,820 --> 00:02:15,460
My name is Lu Shaoyuan.

28
00:02:17,860 --> 00:02:18,820
And this is

29
00:02:19,780 --> 00:02:20,660
Zhuang Yunqiu.

30
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:23,740
What did you say?

31
00:02:25,020 --> 00:02:25,940
Gu Nianchi,

32
00:02:26,700 --> 00:02:28,700
what kind of game are you playing?

33
00:02:29,180 --> 00:02:30,060
Don't forget,

34
00:02:30,700 --> 00:02:33,340
I'm the one who promoted you.

35
00:02:34,460 --> 00:02:36,420
How could I not know who you are?

36
00:02:36,860 --> 00:02:37,940
What did you just say?

37
00:02:38,140 --> 00:02:39,660
Lu Shaoyuan?

38
00:02:41,060 --> 00:02:41,900
Your benefactor.

39
00:02:43,180 --> 00:02:44,779
Wasn't I promoted
to Commander of Yancheng

40
00:02:44,779 --> 00:02:46,400
because of the military merit
I earned back then?

41
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:48,619
If anything, I was the one
who saved your life.

42
00:02:48,620 --> 00:02:49,340
Commander-in-Chief.

43
00:02:49,860 --> 00:02:51,140
That's true.

44
00:02:51,420 --> 00:02:53,899
If you hadn't earned
great military merit back then,

45
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:56,060
you wouldn't be where you are today.

46
00:02:56,340 --> 00:02:58,820
But that also became my greatest regret.

47
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:01,700
If not for that,

48
00:03:02,580 --> 00:03:04,540
my brother would've
never taken my place,

49
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:06,180
and sided with you,

50
00:03:06,860 --> 00:03:09,900
then none of this would've happened.

51
00:03:10,180 --> 00:03:11,140
Your brother?

52
00:03:12,300 --> 00:03:13,940
Are you twins?

53
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:17,100
No...

54
00:03:17,620 --> 00:03:18,700
What are you trying to do?

55
00:03:21,900 --> 00:03:23,020
To seek justice.

56
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:24,860
Commander-in-Chief,

57
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:26,940
shouldn't you

58
00:03:27,340 --> 00:03:29,979
answer for the mistakes

59
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:31,660
you've made

60
00:03:32,060 --> 00:03:33,380
and the lives you've taken?

61
00:03:34,820 --> 00:03:35,420
No.

62
00:03:35,900 --> 00:03:37,299
You've got it all wrong.

63
00:03:37,300 --> 00:03:39,060
None of that was done by me.

64
00:03:39,980 --> 00:03:41,860
You're the mighty Commander-in-Chief.

65
00:03:42,260 --> 00:03:43,860
Was someone forcing you to do it?

66
00:03:44,620 --> 00:03:45,299
Exactly.

67
00:03:45,300 --> 00:03:46,979
As the Commander-in-Chief,

68
00:03:46,980 --> 00:03:48,460
why would I do something like that?

69
00:03:50,940 --> 00:03:51,780
Yes,

70
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:55,420
Gu Nianchi was ordered
to help gather wealth,

71
00:03:55,500 --> 00:03:57,540
but how it was done,

72
00:03:57,860 --> 00:03:59,220
I knew nothing about it.

73
00:04:05,420 --> 00:04:06,900
Do you think saying that

74
00:04:07,980 --> 00:04:10,180
lets you escape responsibility?

75
00:04:13,620 --> 00:04:15,659
It was your indulgence and inaction

76
00:04:15,660 --> 00:04:17,620
that ruined countless innocent lives.

77
00:04:17,980 --> 00:04:19,779
Do you even know

78
00:04:19,780 --> 00:04:23,260
that the wealth and luxury you enjoy
came at the cost of countless lives?

79
00:04:23,860 --> 00:04:24,500
No.

80
00:04:26,180 --> 00:04:27,940
I was wrong.

81
00:04:28,220 --> 00:04:28,980
How about this?

82
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:31,260
I'll give up my position
as Commander-in-Chief.

83
00:04:31,380 --> 00:04:35,180
I'll donate every bit
of wealth I've accumulated to the people.

84
00:04:35,460 --> 00:04:35,859
Oh,

85
00:04:35,860 --> 00:04:38,179
and the Zhuang family as well.

86
00:04:38,180 --> 00:04:40,459
And everyone harmed by Gu Nianchi,

87
00:04:40,460 --> 00:04:42,420
I'll clear their names one by one.

88
00:04:42,540 --> 00:04:43,260
As long as you

89
00:04:43,420 --> 00:04:44,980
spare my life,

90
00:04:45,260 --> 00:04:46,620
I'll do anything.

91
00:04:48,780 --> 00:04:49,340
Darling,

92
00:04:50,580 --> 00:04:51,620
you decide.

93
00:04:55,540 --> 00:04:56,380
Miss Zhuang,

94
00:04:57,180 --> 00:04:58,100
please spare me.

95
00:05:07,060 --> 00:05:10,580
A man like him
dying won't change anything.

96
00:05:12,020 --> 00:05:13,460
Better to do as he said.

97
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:15,940
Have all his wealth donated

98
00:05:16,940 --> 00:05:18,300
to help the people,

99
00:05:19,820 --> 00:05:22,140
clear the names of everyone
who was wronged,

100
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:24,540
and make every guilty person

101
00:05:25,860 --> 00:05:27,380
face justice.

102
00:05:35,220 --> 00:05:36,539
(Lao Fengxiang Jewelry Store)
Extra!

103
00:05:36,540 --> 00:05:38,640
The Zhuang family's smuggling case
has been overturned.

104
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:41,019
Li Shuche has been removed from office
and will stand trial immediately.

105
00:05:41,020 --> 00:05:41,939
Give me a copy.

106
00:05:41,940 --> 00:05:42,979
I want one too.

107
00:05:42,980 --> 00:05:46,580
One for me too.

108
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:53,000
(The Zhuang family's smuggling case
has been overturned.)

109
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:55,800
(Li Shuche has been removed from office
and will stand trial immediately.)

110
00:07:06,140 --> 00:07:06,900
Commander,

111
00:07:07,180 --> 00:07:08,020
are you alright?

112
00:07:24,820 --> 00:07:26,740
Lu Shaoyuan.

113
00:07:26,940 --> 00:07:29,480
(Li Shuche has been removed from office
and will stand trial immediately.)

114
00:07:30,380 --> 00:07:32,540
You got rid of Li Shuche

115
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:37,580
and turned me into a discarded pawn.

116
00:07:42,660 --> 00:07:44,700
But don't get too comfortable.

117
00:07:46,860 --> 00:07:49,940
We'll be seeing
each other again very soon.

118
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:53,900
Is the surgery ready?

119
00:07:55,420 --> 00:07:56,540
Everything is prepared.

120
00:08:05,020 --> 00:08:06,460
(Shaoyuan,)

121
00:08:06,540 --> 00:08:09,860
(you'll soon get to see
your brother, Cheng Yi again.)

122
00:08:15,340 --> 00:08:16,660
What a pity.

123
00:08:19,180 --> 00:08:22,640
(Commander Gu Nianchi achieves
great success in the opium ban.)

124
00:08:27,260 --> 00:08:28,620
What are you laughing about?

125
00:08:30,020 --> 00:08:32,719
I was just thinking,
back when I read the newspapers,

126
00:08:32,719 --> 00:08:34,819
they were always full
of criticism toward the Commander.

127
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:36,000
But now everything has changed.

128
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,540
All they're writing
are praises about you.

129
00:08:40,580 --> 00:08:41,780
It's just a shame

130
00:08:42,100 --> 00:08:44,260
they still think the Commander
is that Gu Shaoyan.

131
00:08:46,300 --> 00:08:47,140
It's alright.

132
00:08:48,380 --> 00:08:50,020
Even if no one else knows,

133
00:08:50,940 --> 00:08:52,340
as long as you do, that's enough.

134
00:08:55,540 --> 00:08:57,420
You've really worked hard these days.

135
00:08:57,660 --> 00:09:00,019
You've been searching for
both Cheng Yi and Gu Shaoyan,

136
00:09:00,020 --> 00:09:01,500
while still handling official duties.

137
00:09:02,020 --> 00:09:03,660
Now that you've
received Cheng Yi's letter,

138
00:09:03,660 --> 00:09:04,900
you must feel much more relieved.

139
00:09:08,700 --> 00:09:11,660
You've been through a lot
staying by my side lately.

140
00:09:13,620 --> 00:09:14,780
A gift was prepared for you.

141
00:09:21,060 --> 00:09:22,420
When did you buy it?

142
00:09:23,980 --> 00:09:25,500
That's a secret.

143
00:09:26,060 --> 00:09:26,980
Try it on.

144
00:09:40,660 --> 00:09:41,460
Do you like it?

145
00:09:45,780 --> 00:09:46,460
I do.

146
00:09:48,340 --> 00:09:51,180
Then is there a reward for me?

147
00:09:54,740 --> 00:09:56,740
(I'm back.)

148
00:10:02,140 --> 00:10:05,740
Didn't expect your taste in shoes
to be this good.

149
00:10:06,940 --> 00:10:11,020
But my taste in people is even better.

150
00:10:19,940 --> 00:10:24,630
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

151
00:10:25,940 --> 00:10:31,260
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

152
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:35,340
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

153
00:10:35,680 --> 00:10:38,690
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

154
00:10:38,860 --> 00:10:43,980
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

155
00:10:45,100 --> 00:10:50,290
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

156
00:10:51,350 --> 00:10:56,950
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

157
00:10:57,490 --> 00:11:00,870
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

158
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:04,069
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

159
00:11:04,070 --> 00:11:09,209
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

160
00:11:09,210 --> 00:11:13,529
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

161
00:11:13,530 --> 00:11:16,109
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

162
00:11:16,110 --> 00:11:18,389
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

163
00:11:18,390 --> 00:11:21,939
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

164
00:11:21,940 --> 00:11:26,469
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

165
00:11:26,470 --> 00:11:29,000
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

166
00:11:29,140 --> 00:11:31,089
♪Still I walk into♪

167
00:11:31,090 --> 00:11:34,689
♪The trap you set without regret♪

168
00:11:34,690 --> 00:11:38,739
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

169
00:11:38,740 --> 00:11:41,319
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

170
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:43,479
♪A stand in can never cross♪

171
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:46,919
♪The shortest distance between us♪

172
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:51,890
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

173
00:11:52,050 --> 00:11:56,720
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

174
00:11:59,500 --> 00:12:01,069
♪A substitute♪

175
00:12:01,070 --> 00:12:06,070
♪Needs no reason♪

